  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Laconia Villa is part of the Blu Hotels collection, its beach side location the rooms are located around the gardens and the central square with a reception and bar.</p>
<p>The hotel allows you time to relax by the pool or explore the local area, <a data-udi="umb://document/bd908f4005884c648b2a31a6ca9bf583" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd908f4005884c648b2a31a6ca9bf583}" title="Cannigione">Cannigione</a> is 2km and the exclusive resort of Porto Cervo is 15km.</p>
<p>Ideal for families the Laconia Village village has a complimentary Mini Club for children aged 4 to 11yrs that operates from 14<sup>th</sup> June until September 13<sup>th</sup> and a Junior Club for those aged 12 – 17yrs between 19 May and 14<sup>th</sup> Sept.</p>]]></description>
